data.description: Beautiful 4 bedroom 3 and 1/2 bath home on over a 1/2 acre of land located in Brookstone subdivision. This brick home has so much to offer. An in ground pool, split floor plan, hardwood flooring, tile, and carpet. Home has two primary bedrooms with full bathrooms garden tub both with dual vanity located on opposite sides of home. Both primary bedrooms have their own exit to the pool in the backyard. Separate dinning area, living room with built in wall of shelves. Quartz countertops with a gas range in the kitchen overlooking the breakfast area and bar with a half bath beside the exit to the pool. Oversized cherry cabinets. Theater.
